AUDIO: 'Have you ever wanted to change your home\'s interior design, but didn\'t know where to start? Maybe a new color for the walls, maybe different furniture, but when you get into the details, [music] you realize how complicated interior design actually is. You have to choose a style, create layouts, know the'

[00:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'prices, and then hope it all turns out well in [music] the end. But now there\'s an AI powered platform that does all of this with just a few clicks. [music] Ideal House. This is where home design becomes a creative and enjoyable game.'

[00:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; [music] &gt;&gt; Just go to Ideal House. It has a clean,'

[00:44] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'elegant interface filled with soft colors and a minimalist design. It truly feels like a professional design studio. You don\'t need any complicated signup process. Simply log in with your Google or Apple account and within seconds'

[00:57] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'you\'ll enter the world of smart design. The mobile version is also available for both Android and iOS so you can design right from your phone. After logging in you\'ll land on the main tools page, AI tools hub. This section is full of'

[01:09] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'exciting features. You can redesign your room\'s interior, change the exterior of your house, design a garden, and even create a full house layout from scratch using new tools like AI floor plan generator and house plan generator.'

[01:21] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'There\'s a simple generate button that does all the work for you, but the real magic begins with House GPT. House GPT is an intelligent interior design assistant that talks to you, gives ideas, suggests colors, and even'

[01:33] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'arranges furniture combinations. For example, you might say, "I want my room to feel happier and more energetic, and it replies, paint one section of the wall bright orange. Use orange as the base color for your bed combined with'

[01:46] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'white and yellow. And for furniture, choose shades of blue." the complimentary color to make the room feel more alive. At that moment, you truly feel like a real designer is sitting beside you. Now, let\'s move on'

[01:58] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'to interior remodel. Just upload a photo of your room. The system lets you choose your favorite style: modern, Scandinavian, classic, or minimalist. Within seconds, a new image is generated based on your selected style. The'

[02:10] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'lighting, wall colors, furniture, and even textures change precisely and naturally. You can switch between styles multiple times until you get the perfect result. Now, it\'s time to take it a step further. If you want to create a'

[02:22] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'complete floor plan of your house, go to the AI floor plan generator. Here, you can customize everything: number of bedrooms, bathrooms, total area, and even whether you want an open or closed kitchen. You can also check options for'

[02:34] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'additional spaces like a garage, home office, or storage. Then, just click generate, and within seconds, you\'ll get a detailed and realistic floor plan as if a professional architect designed it for you. For larger projects, there\'s'

[02:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'also house plan generator which can design multi-story buildings and full home structures. One of the most practical and intelligent features of ideal house is budget estimation. Simply ask, how much would it cost to remodel a'

[02:59] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '150 ft bedroom in a minimalist style and instantly it gives you a detailed table including paint, flooring, lighting, furniture, curtains, and even labor costs. Everything is displayed with real'

[03:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'numbers and prices. This way, before starting the project, you\'ll know exactly how much it will cost and where you can save money. And now comes the most exciting part of Ideal House, the special tools for both designers and'

[03:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'regular users. This is where creativity meets technology. First, let\'s check out furniture try-on. Imagine you have a photo of your room, but you\'re not sure which furniture would match. Just click on add a photo, upload your room image,'

[03:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'then go to the add furniture section to browse different models of sofas, tables, or lamps. You can [music] drag each piece of furniture onto the photo, resize it, rotate it, and even mix multiple items together. You see in real'

[03:51] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'time how each change affects the space as if you\'re rearranging furniture in real life. Next, we have smart replacer. This one\'s incredible. Imagine you don\'t like your couch in a photo or want to change your carpet. Simply select the'

[04:04] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'area and type something like, "Replace the red chair with a blue modern sofa." In just a few seconds, your red chair is replaced with a modern blue one with perfect lighting and shadows. This feature is amazing for creating marketing visuals or previewing your'

[04:17] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'final design. Now, let\'s move to image to video, a completely new tool. Here, you can turn your designed images into realistic videos. Just select an image from your project and AI adds motion, depth, and lighting effects to make it'

[04:29] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'feel like a real video. It\'s perfect for designers who want to showcase their work in portfolio videos or create promotional posts. Imagine having a before and after design. Now, with this tool, you can make a realistic'

[04:41] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'transformation video showing the difference. Alongside these, there\'s also magic editor, which lets you edit images simply by typing text commands. For example, you can type add a plant near the window or change the wall color to pastel green and the changes are'

[04:54] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'applied instantly. Together, all these tools create a complete visual design ecosystem. In the new version of Ideal House, there\'s also a comprehensive feature called House GPT C-Pilot. It guides you step by step through the four'

[05:07] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'main stages of design. Space planning, style and materials, budget estimation, furnishing and styling. From the floor plan to color and material selection, furniture and lighting, everything happens intelligently with live previews. The result, a professional'

[05:20] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'design created in the shortest possible time with maximum precision. With Ideal House, interior design is no longer complex or expensive. Just one photo is enough to redesign your home\'s decor, test new furniture, change wall colors,'

